<h3>Installing [[+packageName]]</h3>

<p>
Go to Extras -> Installer on the main menu in the MODX Manager and click on the &quot;Download Extras&quot; button. That will take you to the
Revolution Repository. Put [[+packageName]] in the search box and press Enter. Click on the &quot;Download&quot; button, and once the package is downloaded,
 click on the &quot;Back to Package Manager&quot; button. That should bring you back to your Package Management grid. Click on the
&quot;Install&quot; button next to [[+packageName]] in the grid. The [[+packageName]] package should now be installed.</p>

